{
  "stem": "10181.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Westerbork is located in sort of the northeastern part of Holland, in an area-- in a province called Drenthe, which was in those days very barren, OK?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were on-- on like [INAUDIBLE], you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The camp was near some farms, but the area was like [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't very open and very close to the German border, but also had very good rail connections.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think that was vital to them, you know, to have the-- the rail-- railroad-- access to railroads.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Approximately when did you all arrive in Westerbork?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1943.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say it was in early spring, probably.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we got to Westerbork, it was on a Monday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why do I know it was a Monday?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the next day-- every Tuesday, there were trains to-- they're the transport to east to Auschwitz, or to Sobibor, which I found out later.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we arrived on a Monday evening, and my cousin and myself were separated from the rest of the family, put up in a different barracks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know if-- if my sister was with my aunt or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know, but I-- she wasn't with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And during the night from this particular barracks, they were called-- people were called to go on the transport the next day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And our name was called also, myself and-- and Alfred's name, very clearly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I know, Fred Spiegel called.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was my name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Alfred Spiegel.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And most of the people in the barracks were called, and most of them-- that's what they often did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They-- you came from one place, and they right of way tried to get rid of you to the-- to-- to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because in Westerbork, people always tried to get to deferment.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
